[t:0x0c0a,n:text]
{
    // First town
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, Stranger. Welcome to Betelgeuse.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "You must be the sibling child of the Lady Luna. She half expected you to come.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "The Lady Luna is with the others at the tents. It's our little tent village, we call it Palim Palim.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Be our guest!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "What took you so long?";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "I'm actually so happy to see you, my dearest!
See what I discovered - the ancient Empire of Stars had contact with Beings from other actual stars! Extraterrestrials! It was an interstellar empire spanning across a whole eight star systems! It's truly incredible!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "What do you mean, you want to go HOME of all places?
...Alright let's go then... But we need to find an Aranna Starstone first...";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "What do you mean, you want to go HOME of all places?
But I don't have an Aranna Starstone...
Anyways I'm staying here. Just look around - this place is amazing!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, friend.
If you are looking for ancient artifacts similar to yours, you should see the Elder of the Lake about them. He lives over in a place called Wishy-Washy, at the Great Lake to the East.
Greet him from me!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "The Elder gave me this stone, long ago, to guard it. I just received a telepathic vision from him telling me to give it to you. The Elder is wise; and I can sense that it will be in good hands.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "I pray for your safe and happy return home.
And whenever you want, come visit us, you'll always be welcome here!
Go with the blessings of the Great Mother.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings to you!
So you come from the stars? Dope.
You know, this place is a paradise for us. Except if you're afraid of spiders, I guess...
Unrelatedly, ...";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings to you!
So you come from the stars? Dope.
You know, this place is a paradise for us. Except if you're afraid of spiders, I guess...";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Would you like me to join you? I'd love to see the stars and stuff... I'm not bad with a bow, which might come in handy. So what do you think?";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, my friend.
I have a few things here that might be useful for you. Come have a look!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, stranger, welcome to Betelgeuse.
Do you happen to be interested in a pack animal? Will come in handy when you go out and find more treasure than you can carry...
I can spare good Dingaling here. She's well-behaved and also brave, she'll defend you and follow you wherever you go.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "I hope Dingaling is doing well?
Sorry, we need the other pack animals ourselves.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, stranger, welcome to Betelgeuse.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "How do you like our Beetles? They're beautiful, aren't they?
We keep them for the delicious Beetlejuice, of course. Fancy a glass?";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, stranger from another star.
So how do you like this planet? Is it much different from yours?
One thing that might be different is our sunlight - Betelgeuse is a pink star. Looks quite pretty ah? I imagine yellow sunlight to look a bit agressive... But to each their own, I guess.
Anyways hope you like it here!";
        to = "";
    }

    // Lake town
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Welcome, youngling. May the blessings of the Great Mother never stop shining upon you.
I sense a great fate on you. No surprise for someone who discovered the old way to the stars, of course.
I also sense that I am destined to give this artifact here to you. May it guide you in your endeavors, and may you use it to mend what has been broken for a millennium.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Our history books tell about the ancient empires. The Utraean Empire and the Empire of Stars were neighbors, and in many ways like siblings - at times allies, at other times rivals. In the end they both crumbled, of course.
Nobody knows how it came that Utraeans live on this planet now - it belonged to the Empire of Stars, of course, not the Utraean Empire. It maybe was fated. It sure is a blessing. I just hope the history behind it wasn't too bloody, hehe.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "There are Utraeans living on your home world as well?
Do greet them from us and send the blessings of the Great Mother. If She wills, we will meet these long-lost siblings one day!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "May the blessings of the Great Mother always shine upon you wherever you go.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Bless you!
Your story sounds amazing! Would you like me coming along? I can do some nature magic...";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Would you like me coming along? I can do some nature magic...";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Bless you!
Your story sounds amazing!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, stranger. I have some equipment here that you might be interested in, have a look... Glad if I can help!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, stranger, welcome to Betelgeuse.
Do you happen to be interested in a pack animal? Will come in handy when you go out and find more treasure than you can carry...
I can spare good Beau here. He's well-behaved and also brave, he'll defend you and follow you wherever you go.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "I hope Beau is doing well?
Sorry, we need the other pack animal ourselves.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, stranger, welcome to Betelgeuse.
Sorry, we need the pack animals ourselves.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Bless-Bless!
Have some Beetlejuice. Hahaha, you look funny. What are all these colors? Have some more Beetlejuice, I say!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Blessings, traveler. Excuse me, I'm a bit dizzy, I've had enough of Beetlejuice for today I guess...";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "So you're new to this planet? It's quite nice ah?
Here we have all we could ever wish for - lots of flowers, a warm pink sun... and the Beetles, of course. Their meat is delicious, but the best thing of course is the Beetlejuice. It's the best of all possible worlds - except if you're afraid of spiders, I guess...";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Have a wonderful day. Enjoy the sun!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Bathing's the best, right?";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Bathing's the best, man.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Come on in, the water is so nice!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "The weather is just wonderful today! To be fair, it always is.";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Such fresh air today... and such warm water. We are truly blessed on this planet!";
        to = "";
    }
    [0x0000]
    {
        from = "Just enjoying the warm rays of our pink sun. Look at Her light on the water! It's so beautiful.";
        to = "";
    }
}
